data.description: Come take a look at this charming home with tons of potential! Boasting 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this residence is an ideal opportunity for those seeking a home with character and the chance to add their personal touch. Step inside to an inviting atmosphere, with a thoughtfully designed layout that enhances the overall flow. The two bedrooms provide comfort and flexibility for residents, offering a peaceful haven for relaxation. The unfinished basement presents an exciting canvas for expansion or customization. Situated on a generous lot, the property allows for outdoor enjoyment, be it gardening, entertaining, or simply soaking in the natural surroundings. The proximity to downtown Columbia ensures easy access to local amenities, dining, and entertainment options. While the home has seen some remodeling, there remains ample room for the new owner to infuse their personal style and preferences into the property. Don't miss out!
